  "original_title": "\u0b86\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "President Ranil will meet the members of the ruling party today",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The first meeting between President Ranil Wickremesinghe and members of the ruling party will take place today at the Ministry of Finance.",
        "Attention will be given to various issues including the next steps of the government and the establishment of an all-party government.",
        "The first meeting between President Ranil Wickremesinghe and members of the ruling party will take place today.",
        "The cabinet comprising 18 ministries was appointed on the 22nd under the leadership of President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Attention will be given to the activities of the new cabinet, the limitation of government expenditure, the formulation and implementation of action plans at the ministerial level to solve the fuel problem.",
        "A member of the ruling party mentioned that the president has insisted that all parties in the government should cooperate with the public to form an all-party government in order to establish a stable government.",
        "Attention has been paid to carry out extensive discussions on the strategy of the All-Party Government, the number of ministries and the issues.",
        "Also, it has been decided to carry out negotiations on principle regarding the unification of opposition parties in an all-party government."
      ],
